Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:49.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:54.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:24.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:30.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:35.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:44.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:50.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:56.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:01.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the 100 million\NBerries we had in here go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that. I gave it to them to buy meat\Nand booze and stuff for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gave it to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:03:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we got a good deal with the ship,\Nso there's no problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami! I'm gonna go out and have fun,\Nso give me some spending money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,@#$%&!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Girl in Search of Her Yagara!\NGreat Search in the City of Water!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Aobire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice of you, Chopper. Thanks for\Ntreating me to this water-water candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! After all,\Nshe did give me 10,000 Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the rest of the money\Nto buy medical books.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! Our town's hero's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa!\N--Yo! Party King!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had fun yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you!\N--Let's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Nami just got done scolding you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,1)}"Missing Yagara"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the way you ate\Nwas really something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really admiring, Party King!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we pick up where we\Nleft off yesterday at my place today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If that's the case, come to my place!\N--That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's coming to my place first!\N--If I remember correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, my place!\N--My place!\N--he's the pirate who saved Iceberg-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--My place!\N--My place!\N--If it's him, maybe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abi! You left without having breakfast again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should give up on finding Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll have him eat at my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We'll have a party at my place first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No! He'll come to my place!\N--Your place is tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family's Yagara went missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me find him... I mean, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's Abi, the photographer's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's still looking for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three days since the Aqua Laguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad, but he's probably gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was already over 100 years old.\NThat big wave was too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lump him with the\Nstupid Yagara you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That big wave wouldn't be\Nenough to take out our Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What'd you say?!\N--Now, now... Calm down, Abi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you say, he might have\Nsurvived the Aqua Laguna,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he hasn't been back for\Nthree days now, so he, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:06:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's right. You shouldn't\Ndrag Straw Hat into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from Water Seven,\Ntoo, so you should know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the story about Yagaras seeking out\Ntheir "final nesting village"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has seen that place,\Nso I'm not gonna believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire appeared in my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Straw Hat! You pirates\Nlove treasure, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all the money I have!\NIf you find him, I'll give it all to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You'll give it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's if you find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't bother, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you, by any chance, come to step\Ninto their final nesting village...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't quite get it, but it is true\Nthat pirates can't just pass up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,treasure that's right in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That treasure of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Abi! Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chopper, our ship's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The little raccoon dog spoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling a little raccoon dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what am I supposed to find again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you listening?!\NAobire! My family's Yagara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know it's him by the blue fin on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His fin is blue, so his name is Aobire, huh?\NI like it. It's easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are we starting our search here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? This is the best place to\Nlook out over the city, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to town already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! I'm here!\NI'm right here! Can't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your act together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one, Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice! It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Nami! Robin!\N--Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. If we ask Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Yagara with a blue fin on his head, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ojos Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Abi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Robin, we now know that\Nhe isn't on the shipbuilding island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The good news is that it saved us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Abi. Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the final nesting village that\Nthe townspeople were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that when Yagaras realize\Ntheir lives are about to end,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they leave their groups or their owners\Nand go to a certain place to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the final nesting village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...\N--But?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if humans see this final nesting village...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they see it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they'll also be taken to the netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a superstition!\NThere's no need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, captain! Do you need\Na sniper for your pirate group?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This humble, flattering plan isn't that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something else...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I got a bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oof! I'm not gonna let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go check the backstreets, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found someone who heard Aobire's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So on the night of the Aqua Laguna,\Nyou heard someone around here say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm coming to rescue you, so hang in there"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says it was definitely\NGrandpa Aobire's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Abi!\N--Yeah! Thank you, little guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredible that you\Nunderstand the Yagara's language!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop it! I'm not a "little guy," you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know that, let's thoroughly\Nsearch this area, shall we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're gonna fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking all over for him, and yet, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Is it warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Watch out! Not that direction, Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, is it true that Aobire can't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's an old Yagara who\Nturned 100 a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that there's no chance\Nthat his sight will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire has been serving our\Nfamily very well for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can no longer deny\Nthe decline in his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should start preparing ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I don't know how\Nbest to explain it to Abi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Aobire's coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take him to the evacuation facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do this every year. You should know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our house is in the center of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he'll be swallowed\Nby the Aqua Laguna, Abi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he really was\Nswallowed by the Aqua Laguna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fish would drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked you to help him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you shouldn't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Abi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can cry later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! We know the\Narea we should be searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:13:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Aobire's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it come from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an entrance to the\Nunderground waterways!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Aobire!\N--Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where are you?!\N--Aobire!\N--Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go any farther on the Yagara like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no water ahead of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, let's try moving ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here and wait for us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? There's a town\Nunderneath the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad told me once that they built\Nnew buildings above the old ones
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and kept doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Abi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see him soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Little guy! Are you guys okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Abi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... Aobire is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the same place that I saw in my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... this is the final nesting village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be right! The final\Nnesting village is a superstition!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like Aobire is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a story created to\Nexplain mysteries about the Yagaras!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! So you were there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire! Come here! Let's go home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says, "I'm sorry, Abi."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?!\NI wanted to see you all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not mad about\Nyour sudden disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that! Let's go home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Now I can feel at ease."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thanks for everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were always together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you to the final nesting village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's that?\N--A Yagara's voice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His heartbeat is weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I think he'll be able to pull through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the scarf kept him\Nwarm and helped him survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's the scarf that I gave to Aobire...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll rescue you now, so hang in there!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Aobire tried to save him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he appeared in my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I couldn't keep my promise, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you two,\NI was able to see Aobire again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I was able to grant his last wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to save this baby Yagara, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll need lots of food in\Norder to get strong, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think that place\Nwas the final nesting village?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the world is full of mysteries\Nthat we know nothing about!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, everyone!\NWe're gonna go shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. I have nothing to do\Nwith you guys! Why do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, carry the younger ones on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I can carry two babies on my back...\NHey, that's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:22:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mothers Are Strong!\NZoro's Hectic Household Chores!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
